import React from 'react'
import { Image, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native'
import {  View, FormControl, Stack, Input, Box, Flex } from 'native-base'

export default function Home() {
  return <View w="90%" maxWidth="300px">
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label fontWeight={'bold'}>Value A</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} />
          <FormControl.Label marginTop={'20px'} fontWeight={'bold'}>Value B</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
        <Box flex='1'>
            <Flex direction='row'>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 2.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 2.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 2.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </Flex>
        </Box>
    </View>
}
